      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Side sill garnish removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Work shall be performed so as not to damage the body or the parts to be removed."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Side sill garnish removal"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Remove the clips (A and B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "2510_3.0_jpn_11581510_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "2",
      "text": "Pull the side sill garnish (A) toward the front of the vehicle and remove it. Remove clips (B and C) from the body. Turn clip C 45° to remove it from the body."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "2510_3.0_jpn_11581511_3.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "attention",
      "items": [
        "Work so as not to damage the body and the parts to which it is attached."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Side sill garnish installation"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Attach the clips (B, C) to the side sill garnish (A). Install the side sill garnish."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "2510_3.0_jpn_11589054_2.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        {
          "text": "Inspect clips for damage and whitening and replace if necessary."
        },
        {
          "text": "Inspect clips for damage and whitening and replace if necessary."
        },
        {
          "text": "Clips should be set securely to prevent floating."
        },
        {
          "text": "Clips should be set securely to prevent floating."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "3",
      "text": "Install clips (A, B)."
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "2510_3.0_jpn_11581513_3.0_disp.png"
    }
